286
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:10,240
And my unfilial daughter,

287
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:12,480
wanting to find information about Shen Yue,

288
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,920
went to Renyi Manor first.

289
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,040
But the old manor master

290
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:18,840
mysteriously died at that time.

291
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:21,440
If not her, then who could it be?

292
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,880
Am I right,

293
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:24,120
my daughter?

294
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:29,400
Bai Feifei.

295
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:32,610
Did the old manor lord really die by your hand?

296
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:40,320
That's right.

297
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,840
I killed Li Changqing.

298
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:44,280
Today,

299
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,100
it will be the same.

300
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:13,380
No matter if this Chai Yuguan is real or fake,

301
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,600
today I

302
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:19,200
want to tell the entire Zhongzhou.

303
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,080
I, Bai Feifei.

304
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,960
I must kill Chai Yuguan.

305
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,400
Stop her!

306
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:44,320
Master Li reversed his blood flow

307
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,520
