308
00:14:45,680 --> 00:14:47,360
It had nothing to do with Bai Feifei.

309
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,880
How could she not be involved?

310
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,800
When all is said and done,

311
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:50,930
it was because of me.

312
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:52,720
Master Leng,

313
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:53,840
to be honest,

314
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:55,200
my real name is Shen Yue,

315
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,600
son of Shen Tianjun.

316
00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:58,040
Master Li's death

317
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:00,320
was to help conceal my identity.

318
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,000
Tell me

319
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,680
where the person who killed my mother

320
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:05,640
is now.

321
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,360
Fate is cruel,

322
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:09,800
Master Li.

323
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:14,320
Miss.

324
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:16,480
I beg for your forgiveness.

325
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,120
Young Hero Shen.

326
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,320
So it seems

327
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:22,980
there's a deep blood feud between your parents.

328
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:26,320
If you insist on protecting this witch today,

329
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:28,040
you'll be opposing the entire righteous martial arts world

330
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:30,240
and all the prestigious sects!

331
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:34,200
Righteous martial arts world?

332
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,330
Prestigious sects?

333
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:38,250
When all is said and done, we are merely

334
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:41,400
a group of mediocre people barking at shadows.

335
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,530
Grudges and righteousness

336
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:45,600
may be important in the martial world,

337
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,080
but for me,

338
00:15:47,640 --> 00:15:48,900
the bond before my eyes

339
00:15:49,280 --> 00:15:50,360
is priceless.

340
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:53,400
The current master of Ghost Palace, Bai Feifei,

341
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:54,880
is my wife.

342
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:58,090
I will not allow anyone to trouble her.

343
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,000
Young Hero Shen,

344
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:11,560
when the old master passed away,

345
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:14,000
you made a hundred-day promise.

346
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:16,290
Now that the truth is revealed,

347
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:17,960
what about your promise?

348
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:19,440
On the day I made that promise,

349
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,280
I did not know.

350
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:22,560
The Invincible Mirror originally belonged to Ghost Palace.

351
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:24,890
Now it has returned to Bai Feifei's hands,

352
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:26,800
it has simply returned to its rightful owner.

353
00:16:26,800 --> 00:16:28,440
I have indeed broken my promise

354
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,760
and cannot escape blame.

355
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,840
But if someone must be held accountable,

356
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,440
I alone will bear the responsibility.

357
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,040
Shen Lang,

358
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:36,560
we've already cut ties completely.

359
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:37,560
My affairs

360
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:40,130
have nothing to do with you.

361
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,200
You may not acknowledge me,

362
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,330
that's your choice.

363
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:47,800
But my not failing you

364
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:48,720
is my choice.

365
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:52,180
I have long had no expectations in this life,

366
00:16:52,400 --> 00:16:53,160
but you alone

367
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:54,320
I cannot let go.

368
00:16:57,800 --> 00:16:59,060
It was your appearance

369
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:01,170
that brought change to my life.

370
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:06,000
So no matter what terrible troubles you cause,

371
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,800
I am willing to bear them for you.

372
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:20,480
Shen Lang,

373
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:23,359
you cannot bear this burden.

374
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:39,410
I, Shen Lang,

375
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:42,370
am willing to give up my martial arts today

376
00:17:42,560 --> 00:17:44,090
and apologize to Master Li.

377
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:46,920
No way.

378
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:47,680
Shen Lang.

379
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:51,560
Shen Lang.
